name: sre_yield
raw_meta_yaml:
{% set name = "sre_yield" %}
{% set version = "1.2" %}


package:
  name: {{ name|lower }}
  version: {{ version }}

source:
  url: https://pypi.io/packages/source/{{ name[0] }}/{{ name }}/sre_yield-{{ version }}.tar.gz
  sha256: e94f1a2a3cbafffe1dcd15c1d54e401a1517e052aa64c7d3164f88dc761d7b8a

build:
  number: 3
  noarch: python
  entry_points:
    - demo_sre_yield=sre_yield:main
  script: {{ PYTHON }} -m pip install . -vv

requirements:
  host:
    - python >=3.6
    - pip
  run:
    - python >=3.6

test:
  imports:
    - sre_yield
    - sre_yield.tests
  commands:
    - pip check
    - demo_sre_yield --help
  requires:
    - pip

about:
  home: https://github.com/google/sre_yield
  license: Apache-2.0
  license_family: APACHE
  license_file: LICENSE
  summary: 'Python module to generate regular all expression matches'
  dev_url: https://github.com/google/sre_yield

extra:
  recipe-maintainers:
    - GianmP94
